                Mesta Di<lb break="no" n="2"/>dae Sit<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> XX <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Lucius Dic<lb break="no" n="6"/>conis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> con<lb break="no" n="7"/>iunx et Dida <lb n="8"/>Sit<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> pater et Mes<lb break="no" n="9"/>cena mater et Sita <lb n="10"/>Mesti avius et <lb n="11"/>Mania avia <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iissimae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stein in spätantikem Grab in Kuklovec zweitverwendet. Teilweise Spuren roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Über dem Inschriftfeld Relief mit Gelageszene.</p>
